{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Istilah Komik Dari Berbagai Belahan Dunia","content":"<p>Pasti bro sis pernah denger istilah komik yang macem-macem dan aneh-aneh dari berbagai bahasa di dunia. Padahal artinya sama aja loh.. Yang bedain cuma penamaan dan sejarah di balik itu. Pernah denger yang namanya Manhua? Mungkin bro sis udah pernah denger, tapi pasti masih banyak yang belom tahu juga kan? Sekarang kita bakal bahas satu-satu istilah dari berbagai belahan dunia yah.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_363\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-363\" data-attachment-id=\"363\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/attachment/manga6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: catatanwisata.files.wordpress.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-363\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga6.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: catatanwisata.files.wordpress.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-363\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: catatanwisata.files.wordpress.com</p></div>\n<ol>\n<li>Manga</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Kalau yang satu ini pasti Kamu udah bisa nebak, istilah satu ini berasal dari Jepang yah guys.. Arti dari manga sendiri bisa merujuk ke animasi dan komik. Di kamus Bahasa Inggris, manga juga berarti komik Jepang. Manga biasanya dibaca dari kanan ke kiri. wah info baru nih untuk yang mau baca manga versi asli.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_364\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-364\" data-attachment-id=\"364\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/attachment/manga5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;&#8220;Many Ways of Doing Business&#8221; by Lu Shaofei (Sumber: nickstember.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-364\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga5.jpg\" alt=\"&quot;Many Ways of Doing Business&quot; by Lu Shaofei (Sumber: nickstember.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-364\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">&#8220;Many Ways of Doing Business&#8221; by Lu Shaofei (Sumber: nickstember.com)</p></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Manhua</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Istilah yang satu ini berasal dari Cina. Orang-orang Cina menyebut komik dengan istilah manhua. Baca manhua biasanya dari kiri ke kanan, atau atas dan bawah.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_365\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-365\" data-attachment-id=\"365\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/attachment/manga2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;The first woodcut manhwa, published in 1908 (Sumber: en.wikipedia.org)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-365\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga2.jpg\" alt=\"The first woodcut manhwa, published in 1908 (Sumber: en.wikipedia.org)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-365\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The first woodcut manhwa, published in 1908 (Sumber: en.wikipedia.org)</p></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Manhwa</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Untuk yang satu ini mungkin udah ga terlalu asing buat kamu yang sering nonton drama Korea atau ngefans banget sama Korea-Koreaan, karena istilah yang satu ini berasal dari Korea. Nah apa sih yang ngebedain dari komik yang lain? Pastinya dari cerita dan style, karena hal tersebut dipengaruhi unsur budaya dan tren yang sedang berkembang di tempat tersebut.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_366\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-366\" data-attachment-id=\"366\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/attachment/manga3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Les Pieds Nickeles (Sumber: en.wikipedia.org)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-366\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga3.jpg\" alt=\"Les Pieds Nickeles (Sumber: en.wikipedia.org)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-366\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Les Pieds Nickeles (Sumber: en.wikipedia.org)</p></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Bande Dessinée</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Yang satu ini sama kaya kita nyebutin pemeran dari film Dr.Strange, ribet! Benedict Cumberbatch. Nahkan ribet bacanya hehe.. Istilah yang satu ini sebenarnya berasal dari Belgia, namun sangat berkembang di Prancis dan meraih sukses yang luar biasa. Beberapa penulis seperti: André Franquin : (Spirou et Fantasio; Marsupilami; Gaston Lagaffe), Morris : (Lucky Luke; Peyo), Jean Graton : (Michel Vaillant) sempat menjadi bintangnya komik Eropa pada saat itu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_367\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-367\" data-attachment-id=\"367\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/attachment/manga4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Komik Put On&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-367\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga4.jpg\" alt=\"Komik Put On\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-367\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Komik Put On</p></div>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Komik</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Inilah istilah di Indonesia yang sering kita gunakan. Komik adalah turunan kata dari Bahasa Inggris yaitu comic. Di Indonesia, komik mulai eksis sejak kehadiran komik strip Put On pada harian Sin Po sekitar tahun 30an. Hingga hari ini, para komikus Indonesia bergantian lahir dan mengisi jagad perkomikan tanah air.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_368\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-368\" data-attachment-id=\"368\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/istilah-komik-dari-berbagai-belahan-dunia/attachment/manga1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-368\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga1.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Manga1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-368\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">CIAYO Comics</p></div>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>Komik Digital / Komik Webtoon</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Pasti udah nggak asing buat kamu yang punya hape pintar, karena kebanyakan webtoon atau komik digital ini sering dibaca sama kamu yang lagi nunggu sesuatu. Contohnya nunggu bis, nunggu kelas pas kuliah, atau lagi nunggu pacar dandan. Sekarang udah banyak platform komik Indonesia untuk baca komik digital Indonesia. Salah satunya CIAYO Comics. Di sini kamu bisa langsung baca komik webtoon Indonesia yang kamu mau sesuai dengan genre yang kamu suka, kayak horor, komik drama, slice of life dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b41409f0-2cdd-5980-b4d6-09057d8139be"}}}